---
title: Lamb Rump & Baby Potato Dauphinoise with Red Wine Jus & Green Bean Kale Salad
description: Celebrate the season with a succulent lamb rump, served alongside rich, creamy baby potato dauphinoise and a luscious red wine jus. Paired with a vibrant green bean and kale salad, this festive dish is the perfect blend of indulgence and holiday cheer!
